    "These two approaches are NLP-based text segmentation methods applied to 1D molecular representation encoding (e.g., SMILES and SELFIES).",
    "These methods had some good results in the field of NLP 32, 33, at the same time, through the test at hand in the interaction prediction task also has good performance.",
    "Selection of molecular fragment.",
    "When the purpose of molecular fragmentation is to facilitate molecular representation, the selection of fragments after splitting becomes particularly crucial.",
    "The screening of the fragment library generated through fragmentation is a vital step to obtain high-quality fragments."
